<content5 releasenbr="1">
<step1>
<ptxt>CONSTRUCTION</ptxt>
<step2>
<ptxt>Manual Tilt Mechanism</ptxt>
<step3>
<ptxt>The manual tilt mechanism allows adjustment of the steering wheel position in the vertical direction through lever operation. This provides the driver with the most comfortable driving position.</ptxt>
</step3>
<step3>
<ptxt>The manual tilt mechanism is locked using the tilt lever.</ptxt>
